cs.LG, cs.CR, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SI 

This paper discusses the generalization properties of GANs and evaluates their information leakage, which are topics related to machine learning (cs.LG), privacy protection (cs.CR), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and social and information networks (cs.SI). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
